Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许侵犯个人隐私绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你发过短信吧
