Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上星期发来的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上星期？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还分了3条让人超不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
